        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "Harry's heart and judgment alike responded to the call.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_244435_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/244435/6295_244435_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "\"This is your discharge from the Palmetto Guards,\" he said.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_244435_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/244435/6295_244435_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "\"Colonel Kenton writes wisely.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_244435_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/244435/6295_244435_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "I shall look for you there.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_244435_000023_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/244435/6295_244435_000023_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "His manner was much more considered and grave.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_244435_000024_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/244435/6295_244435_000024_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "The very triumph and joy of living penetrated his soul. Youth swept aside the terrors of war.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_244435_000026_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/244435/6295_244435_000026_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "All the winds blew in the same direction in South Carolina and they sang one song of triumph, but in Kentucky they were variable and conflicting, and their voices were many.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_244435_000027_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/244435/6295_244435_000027_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "People were cooler here and they were more prone to look at the two sides of a question.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_244435_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/244435/6295_244435_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "It was afternoon when he reached the little station of Winton and left the train, a tall, sturdy boy, the superior of many a man in size, strength and agility.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_244435_000029_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/244435/6295_244435_000029_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "You were at the bombardment of Fort Sumter, they tell me! It's made a mighty stir in these parts!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_244435_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/244435/6295_244435_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "\"Look out for what?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_244435_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/244435/6295_244435_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "\"I will,\" replied Harry, with vivid recollection of his ride from Pendleton to Winton.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_244435_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/244435/6295_244435_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "\"If you've got pistols, just you think once before you shoot,\" said Collins.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_244435_000037_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/244435/6295_244435_000037_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "He had little fear.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_244435_000038_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/244435/6295_244435_000038_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "This was not the fashion of a year ago, when they exchanged a friendly word or two, but Harry knew its cause.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_244435_000039_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/244435/6295_244435_000039_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "But he saw nothing that moved there.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_64301_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/64301/6295_64301_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "A CATASTROPHE.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_64301_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/64301/6295_64301_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "One winter evening, as soon as his work was over for the day, Joseph locked the door of his smithy, washed himself well, put on clean clothes, and, taking his violin, set out for Testbridge: Mary was expecting him to tea.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_64301_000002_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/64301/6295_64301_000002_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "It was the afternoon of a holiday, and she had closed early.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_64301_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/64301/6295_64301_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "His being was like an all sided lens concentrating all joys in the one heart of his consciousness.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_64301_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/64301/6295_64301_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "Earth was gone, and heaven was all.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_64301_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/64301/6295_64301_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "When he reached the suburbs, the light of homes was shining through curtains of all colors.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_64301_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/64301/6295_64301_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "When he reached Mary's shop, he turned into the court to the kitchen door.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_64301_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/64301/6295_64301_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "\"Through the kitchen to the parlor!\" he said.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_64301_000007_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/64301/6295_64301_000007_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "O my God-through the mud of me, up to thy righteousness!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_64301_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/64301/6295_64301_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "Mary came half-way to meet him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_64301_000009_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/64301/6295_64301_000009_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "He stepped across the floor, still, stately, and free.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_64301_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/64301/6295_64301_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "Letty, finding herself not quite equal to the emergency, came in her turn to call Mary: she went as quietly as if she were leaving a tiresome visitor.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_64301_000010_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/64301/6295_64301_000010_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "The music was broken, and Joseph left alone with the dumb instruments.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_64301_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/64301/6295_64301_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "Mary had not listened long before she found herself strangely moved. Her heart seemed to swell up into her throat, and it was all she could do to keep from weeping.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_64301_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/64301/6295_64301_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "A little longer and she was compelled to yield, and the silent tears flowed freely.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_64301_000012_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/64301/6295_64301_000012_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "Letty, too, was overcome-more than ever she had been by music.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_64301_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/64301/6295_64301_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "A mood had taken shape in the mind of the blacksmith, and wandered from its home, seeking another country.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_64301_000013_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/64301/6295_64301_000013_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "Thus, in a garment of mood whose color and texture was music, did the soul of Joseph Jasper that evening, like a homeless ghost, come knocking at the door of Mary Marston.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_64301_000013_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/64301/6295_64301_000013_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "It prayed, it wept, it implored.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6295_64301_000013_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6295/64301/6295_64301_000013_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6295",
        "content": "It cried aloud that eternity was very long, and like a great palace without a quiet room.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
